!! For the initials of contributors, see ~abinit/doc/developers/contributors.txt .
!!
!! CHILDREN
!! contract_dp_ge_val.F90
!! contract_int_ge_val.F90
!! contract_int_le_val.F90
!! contract_int_list.F90
!!
!!***
